
Requirements
------------

The sloc project has a number of software dependencies.

deal.II_ is a finite element differential equations analysis library.

FLANN_ is a library for performing fast approximate nearest neighbor
searches in high dimensional spaces.

CGAL_ is a computational geometry algorithms library.

.. _deal.II: http://www.dealii.org/
.. _FLANN: https://github.com/mariusmuja/flann
.. _CGAL: http://www.cgal.org/


Installation Procedure
----------------------

Installing deal.II was done as follows::
    $ cd ~/dev/
    $ svn co svn co http://www.dealii.org/svn/dealii/trunk/deal.II
    $ cd deal.II
    $ ./configure
    $ make all

Installing FLANN::
    $ cd ~/dev/
    $ git clone --depth=1 git://github.com/mariusmuja/flann.git
    $ cd flann
    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make

Installing CGAL::
    $ cd ~/src/
    $ tar xvfz CGAL-3.9.tar.gz
    $ cd CGAL-3.9
    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make


